  "title": "Cold Truck Driver",
  "description": "<h3>Job Responsibilities:</h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>Safely operate cold trucks to transport frozen and chilled goods.</li>\n  <li>Ensure timely and accurate delivery to designated locations.</li>\n  <li>Handle loading and unloading of goods with care.</li>\n  <li>Maintain vehicle cleanliness and report any issues promptly.</li>\n  <li>Comply with all road safety and company regulations.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Job Requirements:</h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>Preferably Singaporean or PR.</li>\n  <li>Possess a valid Class 3 or 4 driving licence.</li>\n  <li>Prior experience in cold truck or goods delivery driving is an advantage.</li>\n  <li>Physically fit, responsible, and punctual.</li>\n  <li>Able to work independently with minimal supervision.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>What We Offer:</h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>Competitive salary and benefits package.</li>\n  <li>Opportunities for career advancement.</li>\n  <li>A collaborative and supportive work environment.</li>\n</ul>",
